Package sample.models

Class Appointments

java.lang.Object
sample.models.Appointments
public class Appointments extends Object
The Appointments class represents an appointment with various properties such as ID, title, description, location, type, start and end times, customer ID, user ID, and contact ID. It provides getters and setters for accessing and modifying the properties.
Author:
Antonio Jenkins
